'''Krath''' was a fictional character from children's fairy tales that were popular around the time of the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]]. He was portrayed as an evil [[Magic/Legends|magician]]-[[God/Legends|god]].<ref name="uprising1">[[Tales of the Jedi – The Freedon Nadd Uprising 1|''Tales of the Jedi – The Freedon Nadd Uprising'' 1]]</ref>

Tales about Krath were told to the [[Keto]] cousins during their youths. When the two [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitive]] relatives grew up and were lured to the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side of the Force]], they founded a dark-side secret society and named it the '[[Krath/Legends|Krath]]' after the character.<ref name="uprising1" />
